# Neighbor-Joining Phylogenetic Tree

## Input Files

- `line.info.salicornia2025.txt`
- `kmer_matrix.319.salicornia_accessions.filtered.5.percent.maf.txt`

## Usage

Run `Salicornia.phylogenetic.tree.R` using the input files above to generate:

- **Figure 4:** Fan-style neighbor-joining (NJ) phylogenetic tree.
- **Extended Data Fig. 7:** Circular neighbor-joining (NJ) phylogenetic tree.
